1261
02:09:43,839 --> 02:09:44,897
Stop.

1262
02:09:46,142 --> 02:09:47,905
-Jung-ile.
-Ano?

1263
02:09:48,577 --> 02:09:50,704
-Seš trpaslík, že?
-Ano.

1264
02:09:52,515 --> 02:09:53,948
Řekni "Já jsem trpaslík."

1265
02:09:55,818 --> 02:09:58,912
-No tak, řekni "Já jsem trapslík."
